D R Horton Realty of NW Florida, LLC

data.description: Home sweet Home!!! (NEW ROOF 2019) If you are looking for a home in a peaceful country environment but yet convenient to town, this home is just perfect for you... Nestled in a quiet and restful neighborhood, mere minutes away from Downtown Milton, Hwy 90, I-10, NAS Whiting Field and... Black Water River; this beautiful 3BD/2BA home has a lot to offer. As you walk your way toward the house, you will appreciate the view of the large front yard and its beautiful Palm trees. As you enter the foyer, you are greeted with the large and open Great Room, which includes a cathedral ceiling and the spacious Dining area will welcome your whole family for your gathering evenings. The kitchen which features a beautiful octagonal window that overlooks the front yard and allows soul-refreshing sunlight to get in, offers plenty of cabinets, yards of counter-tops, a nice pantry and a large breakfast nook where you will have the choice to sit and enjoy breakfast, lunch or diner. Conveniently located, next to the Master Suite, the inside laundry includes a washer and a dryer and some extra space for multiple uses. The split Master Suite with its beautiful trey ceiling includes a ceiling fan and an in-suite bath with double vanity, a garden tub/shower combo and his and hers spacious walk-in closets. Two additional bedrooms are part of the home and each one of them includes a closet . A nice full bath conveniently serves both bedrooms.  Extras include a 2 car garage and a HUGE, beautiful backyard that you will enjoy on your lazy Sunday afternoons, either relaxing in your hammock or cooking-out with friends. Schedule your private showing today and be aware, you will fall in love!
